@startuml
[*] -> PowerOnCheck : check if everything is working upon power-on
PowerOnCheck : problem during startup --> StartupFailure : stop system
PowerOnCheck : everything fine during startup --> ReadyToUse : become ready to use
ReadyToUse -> Reset : allow user to reset it when ready to use
ReadyToUse -> Activate : allow user to activate it when ready to use
ReadyToUse -> TurnOff : allow user to turn it off when ready to use
Activate -> MonitoringStart : start monitoring if activated
MonitoringStart -> AlarmTriggered : start the alarm and send alerts if a sensor is triggered during monitoring
AlarmTriggered -> FalseAlarmOrTimeEnds : continue monitoring if it turns out to be a false alarm or the time ends
FalseAlarmOrTimeEnds -> ReadyToUse : return to ready to use state
ReadyToUse -> EnterPassword : stop and return to normal when user enters password at any time
@enduml
